translation: That was mean, Zero! That was mean!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: That was mean, Zero! That was mean!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: You can whine at me later.{#Name="Zero"}
source: You can whine at me later.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Please. Let's put an end to this here.{#Name="Octa"}
source: Please. Let's put an end to this here.{#Name="Octa"}

translation: What are you doing over there?{#Name="Three"}
source: What are you doing over there?{#Name="Three"}

translation: You might want to pay a little more attention to your surroundings, hmm?{#Name="Three"}
source: You might want to pay a little more attention to your surroundings, hmm?{#Name="Three"}

translation: Because I had grown weary of your conduct, my lady.{#Name="Octa"}
source: Because I had grown weary of your conduct, my lady.{#Name="Octa"}

translation: The way you experimented on people...{#Name="Octa"}
source: The way you experimented on people...{#Name="Octa"}

translation: The way you ruthlessly toyed with their lives...{#Name="Octa"}
source: The way you ruthlessly toyed with their lives...{#Name="Octa"}

translation: I simply could not abide it any longer.{#Name="Octa"}
source: I simply could not abide it any longer.{#Name="Octa"}

translation: Your recreational activities{LF}drove me away, my lady.{#Name="Octa"}
source: Your recreational activities{LF}drove me away, my lady.{#Name="Octa"}

translation: So this is your final decision, Octa?{#Name="Three"}
source: So this is your final decision, Octa?{#Name="Three"}

translation: It is. I serve Lady Zero in all things now.{#Name="Octa"}
source: It is. I serve Lady Zero in all things now.{#Name="Octa"}

translation: My lady, you must put an end to these atrocities—{#Name="Octa"}
source: My lady, you must put an end to these atrocities—{#Name="Octa"}

translation: You seem to be somewhat confused, Octa.{#Name="Three"}
source: You seem to be somewhat confused, Octa.{#Name="Three"}

translation: A disciple doesn't choose his Intoner.{#Name="Three"}
source: A disciple doesn't choose his Intoner.{#Name="Three"}

translation: The army of heretics that rejects the natural cycle...{#Name="Octa"}
source: The army of heretics that rejects the natural cycle...{#Name="Octa"}

translation: Render into ash the powers of reason and order!{#Name="Octa"}
source: Render into ash the powers of reason and order!{#Name="Octa"}

translation: I, Octa...summon thee in my name...{#Name="Octa"}
source: I, Octa...summon thee in my name...{#Name="Octa"}

translation: Did you really think...something like that...would finish an Intoner...?{#Name="Three"}
source: Did you really think...something like that...would finish an Intoner...?{#Name="Three"}

translation: Did he really just do that?{#Name="Dito"}
source: Did he really just do that?{#Name="Dito"}

translation: The dragon shows his true colors...{#Name="Decadus"}
source: The dragon shows his true colors...{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: and I was "sent" here by Lady Two.{#Name="Cent"}
source: and I was "sent" here by Lady Two.{#Name="Cent"}

translation: I've come to take this horrid dragon off your hands.{#Name="Cent"}
source: I've come to take this horrid dragon off your hands.{#Name="Cent"}

translation: I'm kind of a busy guy, see?{#Name="Cent"}
source: I'm kind of a busy guy, see?{#Name="Cent"}

translation: In fact, I only had eight hours of sleep last night!{#Name="Cent"}
source: In fact, I only had eight hours of sleep last night!{#Name="Cent"}

translation: If I weren't as powerful as I am...{#Name="Cent"}
source: If I weren't as powerful as I am...{#Name="Cent"}

translation: I'd likely be dead by now.{#Name="Cent"}
source: I'd likely be dead by now.{#Name="Cent"}

translation: And that would be a shame of epic proportions.{#Name="Cent"}
source: And that would be a shame of epic proportions.{#Name="Cent"}

translation: Oh, but listen to me go on!{#Name="Cent"}
source: Oh, but listen to me go on!{#Name="Cent"}

translation: I'm going to be late, and then Lady Two might get angry.{#Name="Cent"}
source: I'm going to be late, and then Lady Two might get angry.{#Name="Cent"}

translation: Not that I'm scared of her or anything. Oh no, nothing like that.{#Name="Cent"}
source: Not that I'm scared of her or anything. Oh no, nothing like that.{#Name="Cent"}

translation: Wouldn't want you to get the wrong idea about me.{#Name="Cent"}
source: Wouldn't want you to get the wrong idea about me.{#Name="Cent"}

translation: Gotta go, kids. Ta-ta for now!{#Name="Cent"}
source: Gotta go, kids. Ta-ta for now!{#Name="Cent"}

translation: Defeat the army of Armisael!{#Name="説明文"}
source: Defeat the army of Armisael!{#Name="説明文"}

translation: What? How the hell did they make it this far!?{#Name="Soldier F"}
source: What? How the hell did they make it this far!?{#Name="Soldier F"}

translation: Look! Octa himself is with them!{#Name="Soldier E"}
source: Look! Octa himself is with them!{#Name="Soldier E"}

translation: All men, take position! Repeat, all men, take position!{#Name="Soldier A"}
source: All men, take position! Repeat, all men, take position!{#Name="Soldier A"}

translation: Look! It's the accursed songstress's slaves of the night!{#Name="Soldier C"}
source: Look! It's the accursed songstress's slaves of the night!{#Name="Soldier C"}

translation: It's the same thing, you idiot!{#Name="Soldier C"}
source: It's the same thing, you idiot!{#Name="Soldier C"}

translation: I...I will protect Lady Three to the very end!{#Name="Soldier G"}
source: I...I will protect Lady Three to the very end!{#Name="Soldier G"}

translation: Well said, kid! You do that! I'm...just gonna let you take the lead, then...{#Name="Soldier B"}
source: Well said, kid! You do that! I'm...just gonna let you take the lead, then...{#Name="Soldier B"}

translation: Keep your eyes on the ground.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Keep your eyes on the ground.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Yes, we don't want to stumble here.{#Name="Decadus"}
source: Yes, we don't want to stumble here.{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: It's not that. Looking at that{LF}dummy just pisses me off.{#Name="Zero"}
source: It's not that. Looking at that{LF}dummy just pisses me off.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: That big baby of yours sure{LF}does get tied up a lot.{#Name="Dito"}
source: That big baby of yours sure{LF}does get tied up a lot.{#Name="Dito"}

translation: If Lady Three catches him, she{LF}may experiment on his body.{#Name="Octa"}
source: If Lady Three catches him, she{LF}may experiment on his body.{#Name="Octa"}

translation: B-Body experiments? Ungh... That would{LF}be delectib... Er, I mean...detestable...{#Name="Decadus"}
source: B-Body experiments? Ungh... That would{LF}be delectib... Er, I mean...detestable...{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: Sorry I messed up again, Zero. I'll be better...{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Sorry I messed up again, Zero. I'll be better...{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: You're not going "Aww!" or "I tried super hard!"{LF}or whatever.{#Name="Zero"}
source: You're not going "Aww!" or "I tried super hard!"{LF}or whatever.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Oh, can I!? Hey, in that case, guess what?{LF}Guess what, huh?{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Oh, can I!? Hey, in that case, guess what?{LF}Guess what, huh?{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Shut it, dummy. The ivy's just gonna dig{LF}deeper into you. Hold still and be quiet{LF}until I can cut you down.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Shut it, dummy. The ivy's just gonna dig{LF}deeper into you. Hold still and be quiet{LF}until I can cut you down.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: I don't think you're telling the truth.{#Name="Three"}
source: I don't think you're telling the truth.{#Name="Three"}

translation: You left because your lust needed{LF}a more eager partner.{#Name="Three"}
source: You left because your lust needed{LF}a more eager partner.{#Name="Three"}

translation: Your limitless desire no longer{LF}caused my honey to flow...{#Name="Three"}
source: Your limitless desire no longer{LF}caused my honey to flow...{#Name="Three"}

translation: That's... Well, it may have been a reason, but...{#Name="Octa"}
source: That's... Well, it may have been a reason, but...{#Name="Octa"}

translation: So tell me, Three...{LF}What does make the old honey flow these days?{#Name="Zero"}
source: So tell me, Three...{LF}What does make the old honey flow these days?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Oh, please. Don't play dumb with me.{LF}I know you have desires.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Oh, please. Don't play dumb with me.{LF}I know you have desires.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: I no longer hold any love for my disciple.{LF}My love is reserved for my soldiers now.{#Name="Three"}
source: I no longer hold any love for my disciple.{LF}My love is reserved for my soldiers now.{#Name="Three"}

translation: You must flee at once!{LF}We cannot stop Lady Three now!{#Name="Octa"}
source: You must flee at once!{LF}We cannot stop Lady Three now!{#Name="Octa"}

translation: Pfft! I'm not scared of some whack-job loser{LF}who hides in her room making dolls all day.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Pfft! I'm not scared of some whack-job loser{LF}who hides in her room making dolls all day.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: They're not dolls, my lady.{LF}They're soldiers she's operated on!{#Name="Octa"}
source: They're not dolls, my lady.{LF}They're soldiers she's operated on!{#Name="Octa"}

translation: Hush. I'm in the middle of something right now.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Hush. I'm in the middle of something right now.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Me too! I'm in the middle of something!{LF}Something weird!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Me too! I'm in the middle of something!{LF}Something weird!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Whenever I look at Three, it's like...{LF}like, my body gets all hot...{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Whenever I look at Three, it's like...{LF}like, my body gets all hot...{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: There's this weird pain in my chest and tummy,{LF}and I start to get all tingly...{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: There's this weird pain in my chest and tummy,{LF}and I start to get all tingly...{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: What should I do, Zero? Am I sick?{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: What should I do, Zero? Am I sick?{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: No, Zero! It's not like that! This is serious!{LF}It's... It's more like...{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: No, Zero! It's not like that! This is serious!{LF}It's... It's more like...{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Ow! Zero, these guys explode!{LF}They explode all over you!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Ow! Zero, these guys explode!{LF}They explode all over you!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Pay attention! Don't let 'em latch on to you!{#Name="Zero"}
source: Pay attention! Don't let 'em latch on to you!{#Name="Zero"}

translation: If the pain's that bad, shake 'em off!{#Name="Zero"}
source: If the pain's that bad, shake 'em off!{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Aaah! Their heads came off! They came off!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Aaah! Their heads came off! They came off!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: That attack looks like it uses up a lot of power.{LF}Wait for an opening and then strike!{#Name="Zero"}
source: That attack looks like it uses up a lot of power.{LF}Wait for an opening and then strike!{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Wait for an opening and then strike!{#Name="Zero"}
source: Wait for an opening and then strike!{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Zerooo! It's too small for me to fly in here!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Zerooo! It's too small for me to fly in here!{#Name="Mikhail"}
